#INSTALLATION#
--------------
# Step 0: clone .vim repository into ~/.vim
> git clone https://github.com/aerowolf01/.vim.git ~/.vim
# Step 1: install plugins using vundle
:BundleInstall
--------------

#MAINTENANCE#
-------------
# Update your plugins
:BundleInstall
-------------

#MODIFICATION#
--------------
# Add a new plugin
Bundle "authorname/reponame"
:BundleInstall
# Remove a plugin
remove plugin folder from .vim/bundle
remove Bundle entry from vimrc
--------------
